# Node JS hain yeh ek tarike se java script ka runtime hain mtlb hame ismen bahut chii achii liberaries milti hain islia hum ise use krte hain jarruri nhi hain agar backend karni hain toh node JS padhni padegi hii , Hum Node JS ko chod kar Deno ya ban bi use kar sakte hain

# hum jyada kaam karna prefer karenge source directory mein kyunki waha par .env mtlb hamare environment variables package.json files sabh aa jaati hain

# Jab hum production par deploy karenge toh yeh environment (.env) variables kaam mein aayaenge 

# actually hamari teen files hoti hain index,app or constant ..... index file mein hamari application start hoti hain jaise ki hamara database connect index file mein h hota hain  , app file mein configurations hoti hain aur cookies hogayi yeh saabh app file mei hota hain , constants iske andar hum restrict karna chahte hain ki yehi chuno yehi options honge yeh bahut important file hoti hain

#  hampe kuch directories structure bhi hote hain
1 DB
2 Models - schema , structure , data ka model
3 Controllers - functionalites yehi likhi jaat hain
4 Routes- /login , /signup
5 Middleware
6 Utils  - utilities ( jaise ek function ko 4 jagah use karna)

