# hampe bahut saari request aati hain jaise get,post,update,delete aur bhii hain ... hum browser mein kuch bhi likhte hain woh mostly get request hoti hain

# (npm init) --- yeh command kaam aati hain tabh hum node package manager se ek appliation ko initialize karte hain npm init karne ke baad yeh hum se question bhi poochta hain par agar hamne likh diya (npm init -y) toh iska mtlb yes hain ki sabko yes kardo jo bhi pooche 

# init ek utility jaise veet aur npm create react thi yeh utlity (init) kaam aati hain poora process batane ke ki package.json file kaise banani hain .. 

# ab jb hum yeh saari cheez kar lenge toh package.json file banegi usmein ekoption hoga scripts waha par text hatakar mein likhunga .... "start" : "node index.js"

# ab iss command ka mtlb hain kii mein jb bhi likhunga npm run start toh meri index.js file chal jayegi

